<div class="container-fluid" style="width:90%">
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12" id="banner">
        <h2>Welcome to McRonald's!</h2>
        <h6>May I take your order?</h6>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <p>
          Who deserves a break today? Apparently you. Below you can peruse the burgers already prepared for you. Nothing
          looks good to you? No problem, you can enter the burger of your choice by typing it in and submitting
          it.<br><br>

          When you're feeling hungry, just click the "Eat Me!"button next to the burger of your choice. Your devoured
          burger will be moved, figuratively speaking, to your stomach-- the right side of your screen.<br><br>

          Click the burger button to begin. It might not be as satisfying as real food, but then again, neither is fast
          food.<br><br>
          <a href="#portfolioPosition"><img src="./assets/img/burger1.png" id="jumperLink"></a>
        </p>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="divider">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-1"></div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <img src="./assets/img/evilRonald.jpg" class="figure-img" />
        <figcaption class="figure-caption-fluid">
          Quit struggling, kid. Obesity and diabetes ain’t so bad and they’re great for business!
        </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-1"></div>
    </div>
  </div> <!-- Jumbotron closes, portfolio begins. -->
  <div class="row">
    <br><br><br><br>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-1"></div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <h4>On The Table</h4>
      <ul>
        {{#each burger}}
        {{#unless this.devoured}}
        <li>
          <button class="change-devoured btn btn-warning mcButton" data-id="{{id}}">Eat Me!</button>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
          {{id}}
          {{burger_name}}</pre><br><br>
        </li>
        {{/unless}}
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <h4>In Your Stomach</h4>
      <ul>
        {{#each burger}}
        {{#if this.devoured}}
        <li>
          {{id}}
          {{burger_name}}</pre><br><br>
        </li>
        {{/if}}
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <footer>
        <h3>Add a Burger</h3>
        <form class="create-form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="burger"></label>
            <input type="text" id="burger" name="burger_name">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning mcButton">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br><br><br><a name="portfolioPosition"></a>

  {{!-- Container Closes --}}
</div>